 The music video was edited by David Blackburn and directed by Joseph Kahn , who also worked with Brown on the " I Can <unk> Ya " and " Forever " videos . The video features American R & B singer <unk> as Brown 's love interest . Kahn had previously directed the video for Britney Spears 's 2008 ' comeback ' song , " <unk> " , after her public breakdown . In an interview with MTV News , Kahn said , " I seem to be the guy that record companies go to when they need help , " he joked . " I truly feel [ Brown ] is <unk> . You don 't drop people just because they made a mistake ( even if it was a big mistake ) . " 
