 = = = <unk> Station = = = 
 
 <unk> Station is the end of the <unk> Line , and trains must continue <unk> along the <unk> Line or the <unk> Line . The latter immediately enters the <unk> Tunnel , allowing the same speeds as the <unk> Line to <unk> . The <unk> Line is only used by the commuter trains to <unk> . Along with building the line , <unk> Station was upgraded from five to six platforms , and also received a new , artistically decorated <unk> between the platforms . The station is located 23 @.@ 16 kilometres ( 14 @.@ 39 mi ) from Oslo Central Station ( Oslo S ) at 104 @.@ 6 metres ( 343 ft ) elevation . 
 
