 On June 15 , 2006 , López was traded to the Boston Red Sox for David <unk> . He posted a 4 @.@ 32 ERA in 14 appearances before getting sent to the <unk> Red Sox of the International League on July 17 because it was too " tough " for the Red Sox to carry a left @-@ handed specialist at that point in the season , according to manager Terry <unk> . He was called up for two short <unk> from July 28 through August 1 and from August 20 through 22 , appearing in one game each time . On September 4 , he was recalled for the remainder of the season . In 11 September <unk> , López allowed only one run . He finished the year going 1 – 0 with a 2 @.@ 70 ERA in 27 games . With <unk> , he had no record and a 4 @.@ 86 ERA in 13 games ( 16 2 ⁄ 3 innings ) . 
 
