 There were 6 @,@ <unk> households out of which 44 @.@ 2 % had children under the age of 18 living with them , 67 @.@ 5 % were married couples living together ( 56 @.@ 1 % of which had children ) , 7 @.@ 2 % had a female <unk> with no husband present , and 22 @.@ 6 % were non @-@ families . 19 @.@ 2 % of all households were made up of individuals and 7 @.@ 9 % had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older . The average household size was 2 @.@ 78 and the average family size was 3 @.@ 21 . 
