 = Alien <unk> = 
 
 Alien <unk> is a platformer video game for Microsoft Windows , Macintosh , Xbox 360 ( through Xbox Live Arcade ) , and PlayStation 3 ( through PlayStation Network ) . It was developed by <unk> Software Productions and published by <unk> Media . Players control an extraterrestrial spider who has crash @-@ landed on Earth , as he seeks to repair his spacecraft and rescue a fellow extraterrestrial spider . 
 <unk> on 8 November 2011 , Alien <unk> was published on 20 March 2013 for the Xbox 360 , Microsoft Windows , and Macintosh , and on 8 May 2013 for the PlayStation 3 . It received mixed to negative reviews upon release ; critics praised the game 's aesthetics but found the gameplay frustrating due to <unk> controls and an <unk> level of <unk> that hampered progression through the game . 
 
 = = Gameplay = = 
 
 Alien <unk> is a physics @-@ based platformer video game . Players control the eponymous <unk> , an extraterrestrial spider , and navigate him through a series of levels that are filled with deadly obstacles . <unk> can run and jump , and has the ability to shoot a web , allowing him to <unk> and swing from object to object within the environment . <unk> throughout each level are a large number of <unk> , which <unk> can collect to score points . <unk> the level quickly , collecting a large number of <unk> , collecting several <unk> in quick succession , and finding score <unk> all increase the player 's score for that level . Players can also lose points by dying , collecting certain <unk> that decrease the player 's score , or going for too long without collecting an <unk> . Players earn between one and five stars on each level , based on their score . Levels are grouped into several stages , including a forest , a pond , a cave system , and outer @-@ space . In order to progress from one stage to the next , players must collect a certain number of stars . Players can collect special power @-@ up <unk> scattered throughout levels . These <unk> allow <unk> to perform feats he is otherwise incapable of , including traveling underwater and jumping to extreme heights . There are 69 levels in the game , and most of them take between 90 seconds and three minutes . 
 
